</p>	

<p class=chptr>
<b>Welcome to the Russian Wodehouse Society &ndash; Twenty Two Years Online!</b></p>
<img src="pix/bazil.gif" border=0 width=106 height=130 alt="StBazil"  style="float:right; margin:12px;">
<p class=gmk4>
<b>The Russian Wodehouse Society</b> is a club with free membership. We are interested in promoting the works of Pelham Grenville Wodehouse.
We popularize the works of Wodehouse among a Russian-speaking audience, gathering together translators, publishers, and fans who are interested in the spread of Wodehouse's works and ideals.
<p class=gmk4>
We host meetings both online and in person, and welcome you to join us! 
<p class=gmk3>
<b><a href="moscow2008.htm">Old Home Week in Moscow</a> 10-16 August 2008</b>
